{"tid":2166495,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"日本內衣廠推出「胸罩口罩」 粉紅蕾絲充斥少女心","createTime":"2020-08-20T12:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T13:06:15.000Z","uid":364392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9814a3a3d4fbcdef3ffd434035c338bba7d6762a","tid":2166495,"uid":364392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"日本內衣廠推出「胸罩口罩」 粉紅蕾絲充斥少女心<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕隨著武漢肺炎疫情持續擴大，多國防疫物資嚴重短缺，對此日本內衣製造商Atsumi Fashion近期開發出外型精美的「胸罩口罩」，在網上引發話題。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，位於富山縣冰見市的Atsumi Fashion，利用原先用於胸罩的不織布素材及立體裁剪技術，生產色彩及樣式都繽紛多元的創意口罩，每日平均量產200副，目前已有2000副配送至當地的市役所。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，胸罩口罩的特徵，除了可以清洗外，穿戴時也能舒適貼合鼻樑，掩蓋口鼻的布料則使用的是對肌膚溫和的綿及聚酯纖維。<br />\n<br />\n出演日本知名影集《雙層公寓》的女星近藤綾，也親自戴上華美的粉紅蕾絲口罩宣傳，前往第一線工廠採訪現況，吸引數名網友直呼「好想要」。<br />\n<br />\nAtsumi Fashion指出，一副口罩可使用約10次左右，洗太多次外型可能會崩壞，現在除了成人尺寸的口罩，還推出素色的孩童尺寸，未來能透過網購方式買到。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3124734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3124734&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5dXdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=43eb1689\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3124734&h=9d89b4a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3124734</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/04/06/phppJ3DxI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F04%2F06%2FphppJ3DxI.jpg&h=a421c5eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5042be8fcd827ac12632dc2df7743bd1ad5bddf","tid":2166495,"uid":36906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T12:48:49.000Z","msg":"點買"},{"pid":"b9f6169612ced32f0867e7de3d14a7b535b3f17